 {
  "text": "Good morning, and welcome to our office. Please come in. Are you here for the meeting on the second floor? Let me help you. First, go straight to the end of this hall. Then turn left. The elevator is on your right. Take the elevator to the second floor, and the meeting room is the first door. Please have a seat there. If you need help, just call me at the reception. Have a great day!",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a16_listening_receptionist.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hello, and welcome! I am so happy you are finally here. Please come in and follow me. This way to the meeting room. Be careful. Go straight, and then turn left at the coffee machine. Here we are. Have a seat, please. Would you like some water or a coffee? Our manager is going to arrive in five minutes. Please make yourself at home. If you need anything, just ask me. Enjoy your visit!",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a16_listening_host.mp3"
 },
